&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://arxiv.org/html/2412.15832v1&quot;&gt;AIFS-CRPS: Ensemble forecasting using a model trained with a loss function based on the Continuous Ranked Probability Score&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/em&gt;, Lang et al.&lt;/li&gt;
